title: Start
body:
Renata: Okay, let's climb this thing!
<<moveToBackground Chair>>
<<detachFrom Chair Renata>>
<<detachFrom Renata Mia>>
<<disableCollisions Mia>>
<<disableCollisions Renata>>
<<moveUp Mia 20 60>>
Mia: Easy does it....
<<moveUp Mia 40 20>>
<<moveUp Mia 40 90>>
<<moveDown Mia 20 120>>
<<moveRight Renata 10 60>>
<<moveRight Mia 40 60>>
<<moveUp Renata 20 60>>
<<moveUp Renata 40 20>>
<<moveUp Renata 40 90>>
<<moveDown Renata 20 120>>
<<enableCollisions Renata>>
<<enableCollisions Mia>>
<<attachTo Renata Mia>>
Renata: We made it over!
[[end]]
